projects.title: inquirio
projects.description: A digital learning platform that gives users access to online courses, certifications etc. Users are able to find educational tools to advance their learning. in addition, the application gives gives people access to further advances while taking courses online. This application takes away the need to do countless research on what are the best resources to be successful in their career field. Instead, they can increase their productivity by navigating through the application and learning in different sources of education.

projects.title: Untapped Island
projects.description: A card collection portfolio for all users who are interested in trading card games. Users can search all cards through a (3rd party Dataset) and add any of their choosing to their portfolio. They can then set them into their portfolio to view and remove if desired. This solves the issue of collecting cards that you own and trying to learn about every feature of each card. This can also help you to easily access cards that you have recently added to your collection into a portfolio of your own without having to manually add all of the featured details yourself, effectively saving you plenty time.

projects.title: Algo Challenger
projects.description: An application that lets users complete code challenges and can view stats of code challenges that they have completed. This gives students and self taught learners another way to challenge themselves through common code. Users can choose which code that they would like to work on, save their choice (favorites Icon), and delete their previous saves.
